title: “We Don’t Live In A Democracy” Blacklisted Journalist Matt Kennard
description:
Matt Kennard is a London based author and journalist. He is head of investigations at the investigative journalism website Declassified UK. He explains in his new book how corporations overthrew democracy. Do you agree? #amazon #corporation #democrats
